snippet.title: Tall Trails Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2393760/Tall_Trails/

Tall Trails is a traversal game about a little guy exploring a vast island chain. Grab items & use them to launch yourself up mountains—the world is full of new ways to explore! Coming 2024, hopefully!

Made by Brady Soglin. Music by Dylan Payne. Voice of Onis McHenry.
